}}|map_alt=|map=File:ArcticCouncil.svg|image=|logo_caption=|logo_alt=左側爲一隻北極狐，右側爲北極爲中心的世界地圖|logo_size=|logo=Arctic Council logo.svg|caption=|alt=|image_size=|homepage={{URL|arctic-council.org|arctic-council.org}}}}'''北極理事會'''（{{lang-en|The Arctic Council}}、{{lang-ru|Арктический совет}}），又译为'''北極議會'''、'''北极委员会'''、'''北极协会'''，是一個高層次國際論壇，關注鄰近[[北極|北極]]的政府和[[原住民|原住民]]所面對的問題。總部設於[[挪威|挪威]][[特羅姆瑟|特羅姆瑟]]。目前組織有八個成員國，分別爲：加拿大、美國、俄羅斯、冰島、挪威、丹麥、瑞典、芬蘭。<ref name="about">{{cite web|title=About the Arctic Council|url=https://arctic-council.org/about/|access-date=September 17, 2021|date=April 7, 2011|publisher=The Arctic Council|archive-date=2022-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220529151058/https://www.arctic-council.org/about/}}</ref>

== 歷史 ==
創立北極理事會的第一步是在1991年由八個鄰近北極的政府所簽署的{{Link-en|北極環境保護策略|Arctic Environmental Protection Strategy}}。在1996年，《渥太華宣言》<ref>{{cite web|title=Arctic Council: Founding Documents|url=http://www.arctic-council.org/index.php/en/document-archive/category/4-founding-documents|access-date=2013-09-05|website=Arctic Council Document Archive|archive-date=2018-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180402223322/http://www.arctic-council.org/index.php/en/document-archive/category/4-founding-documents}}</ref>標誌着理事會的成立，<ref>{{cite web|title=Canada bypasses key players in Arctic meeting|url=https://www.thestar.com/news/canada/2010/03/29/axworthy_canada_bypasses_key_players_in_arctic_meeting.html|access-date=2013-09-05|date=March 29, 2010|last=Axworthy|first=Thomas S.|website=The Toronto Star|archive-date=2022-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220321073504/https://www.thestar.com/news/canada/2010/03/29/axworthy_canada_bypasses_key_players_in_arctic_meeting.html}}</ref>成爲北極國家政府之間合作的論壇，涉及北極土著民族事務、可持續發展和[[环境保护|环境保护]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=Why everyone wants a piece of the Arctic|url=http://www.macleans.ca/2013/05/13/why-the-world-wants-the-arctic/|access-date=2013-09-05|date=May 13, 2013|last=Savage|first=Luiza Ch.|website=Maclean's|publisher=Rogers Digital Media|archive-date=2014-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140305233509/http://www2.macleans.ca/2013/05/13/why-the-world-wants-the-arctic/}}</ref><ref name="Buixade Farre 2014">{{cite journal|title=Commercial Arctic shipping through the Northeast Passage: Routes, resources, governance, technology, and infrastructure|first1=Albert|last2=Stephenson|first2=Scott R.|date=October 16, 2014|journal=[[Polar_Geography|Polar Geography]]|issue=4|doi=10.1080/1088937X.2014.965769|volume=37|pages=298–324|last3=Chen|first3=Linling|last4=Czub|first4=Michael|last5=Dai|first5=Ying|last6=Demchev|first6=Denis|last7=Efimov|first7=Yaroslav|last8=Graczyk|first8=Piotr|last9=Grythe|first9=Henrik|last24=Troein|first22=Jan|last22=Solski|first23=Lingling|last23=Suo|first24=Caroline|first26=Jaap|first25=Vilena|last25=Valeeva|first21=Ivan|last26=van Rijckevorsel|first27=Jonathan|last27=Wighting|last21=Ryzhov|last16=O'Leary|last20=Raspotnik|last14=Matelenok|first10=Kathrin|last10=Keil|first11=Niku|last11=Kivekäs|first12=Naresh|last12=Kumar|first13=Nengye|last13=Liu|first14=Igor|first15=Mari|first20=Andreas|last15=Myksvoll|first16=Derek|last1=Buixadé Farré|first17=Julia|last17=Olsen|first18=Sachin|last18=Pavithran .A.P.|first19=Edward|last19=Petersen|doi-access=free}}</ref>北極理事會還從事[[氣候變遷|氣候變遷]]、化石燃料和北極航船的研究。<ref name="about2">{{cite web|title=About the Arctic Council|url=https://arctic-council.org/about/|access-date=September 17, 2021|date=April 7, 2011|publisher=The Arctic Council|archive-date=2022-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220529151058/https://www.arctic-council.org/about/}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{cite magazine|author=Lawson W Brigham|date=September–October 2021|title=Think Again: The Arctic|url=https://foreignpolicy.com/articles/2010/08/16/think_again_the_arctic?page=full|magazine=Foreign Policy|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131013051820/https://foreignpolicy.com/articles/2010/08/16/think_again_the_arctic?page=full|archive-date=2013-10-13|access-date=2013-09-24}}</ref><ref name="Buixade Farre 2014" /><ref name="AMSA 2009">{{cite book|editor1-first=Lawson|first16=T.|last12=Huntington|first12=H.|last13=Skjoldal|first13=H.|last14=Gold|first14=M.|last15=Williams|first15=M.|last16=Wojhan|last17=Williams|last11=Snyder|first17=M.|last18=Falkingham|first18=J.|title=Arctic marine shipping assessment (AMSA)|url=http://www.arctic.noaa.gov/detect/documents/AMSA_2009_Report_2nd_print.pdf|date=2009|publisher=Protection of the Arctic Marine Environment (PAME), Arctic Council|location=Norway|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160128145221/http://www.arctic.noaa.gov/detect/documents/AMSA_2009_Report_2nd_print.pdf|archive-date=January 28, 2016|first11=J.|first10=B.|editor1-last=Brigham|last4=Barr|editor2-first=V.M.|editor2-last=Santos-Pedro|editor3-first=K.|editor3-last=Juurmaa|last1=Brigham|first1=L.|last2=McCalla|first2=R.|last3=Cunningham|first3=E.|first4=W.|last10=Ellis|last5=VanderZwaag|first5=D.|last6=Chircop|first6=A.|last7=Santos-Pedro|first7=V.M.|last8=MacDonald|first8=R.|last9=Harder|first9=S.|url-status=live}}</ref>

2011年，理事會成員國通過{{Link-en|北極搜索和營救協定|Arctic Search and Rescue Agreement}}，成爲該組織第一份有法律效力的協議。<ref name="about3">{{cite web|title=About the Arctic Council|url=https://arctic-council.org/about/|access-date=September 17, 2021|date=April 7, 2011|publisher=The Arctic Council|archive-date=2022-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220529151058/https://www.arctic-council.org/about/}}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine|author=Lawson W Brigham|date=September–October 2021|title=Think Again: The Arctic|url=https://foreignpolicy.com/articles/2010/08/16/think_again_the_arctic?page=full|magazine=Foreign Policy|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131013051820/https://foreignpolicy.com/articles/2010/08/16/think_again_the_arctic?page=full|archive-date=2013-10-13|access-date=2013-09-24}}</ref><ref name="Buixade Farre 2014" /><ref name=":0" />

2022年3月3日，因[[2022年俄羅斯入侵烏克蘭|2022年俄罗斯入侵乌克兰]]事件，除俄罗斯以外的7个成员国紧急通过视频会议，宣布在俄罗斯作为理事会主席国期间，不参加剩余会议。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Joint Statement on Arctic Council Cooperation following Russia's Invasion of Ukraine|url=https://via.ritzau.dk/pressemeddelelse/joint-statement-on-arctic-council-cooperation-following-russias-invasion-of-ukraine?publisherId=2012662&releaseId=13645015|access-date=3 March 2022|date=3 March 2022|archive-date=2022-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220604082246/https://via.ritzau.dk/pressemeddelelse/joint-statement-on-arctic-council-cooperation-following-russias-invasion-of-ukraine?publisherId=2012662&releaseId=13645015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Canada, six other states pull back from Arctic Council in protest over Ukraine|url=https://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/canada-six-other-states-pull-back-from-arctic-council-in-protest-over-ukraine-1.5804272|date=3 March 2022|website=ctvnews.ca|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220304121942/https://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/canada-six-other-states-pull-back-from-arctic-council-in-protest-over-ukraine-1.5804272|archive-date=3 March 2022|url-status=live}}</ref>

== 會籍 ==

=== 國家 ===

==== 成員 ====
按照規定，只有有部分領土位於北極圈內的國家方可成為正式成員，現在北極理事會的成員有：<ref name="about4">{{cite web|title=About the Arctic Council|url=https://arctic-council.org/about/|access-date=September 17, 2021|date=April 7, 2011|publisher=The Arctic Council|archive-date=2022-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220529151058/https://www.arctic-council.org/about/}}</ref>

* {{Flag|Canada}}
* {{Flag|Denmark}}(包括屬土{{Flag|Greenland}}及{{Flag|Faroe Islands}})
* {{Flag|Finland}}
* {{Flag|Iceland}}
* {{Flag|Norway}}
* {{Flag|Russia}}
* {{Flag|Sweden}}
* {{Flag|United States}}

==== 正式觀察員 ====
北極理事會設置觀察員席，對非北極國家開放，由每兩年舉辦一次的部長會議所決定。觀察員無投票權。截至2021年，共有13個非北極國家獲觀察員地位。<ref name="arcticcouncilobservers">{{cite web|title=Observers|url=https://arctic-council.org/about/observers/|access-date=September 15, 2021|publisher=Arctic Council Secretariat (2021). Arctic Council|archive-date=2022-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220529151107/https://www.arctic-council.org/about/observers/}}</ref>觀察員通常會受邀參加理事會的絕大部分會議，雖然部分非北極國家希望能夠加入一些深部的內部活動，但觀察員並非一定能夠參加某些項目和任務。

* 1998年加入：
** {{Flag|Germany}}
** {{Flag|Netherlands}}
** {{Flag|Poland}}
** {{Flag|United Kingdom}}
* 2000年加入：
** {{Flag|France}}
* 2006年加入
** {{Flag|Spain}}
* 2013年5月15日，在[[瑞典|瑞典]]北部城市[[基律纳|基律纳]]召开的北极理事会第八次部长级会议上，以下國家加入：<ref>{{Cite web|title=中国成为北极理事会正式观察员|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2013-05/15/c_115782682.htm|accessdate=2013-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130924071156/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2013-05/15/c_115782682.htm|archive-date=2013-09-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>
** {{Flag|China}}
** {{Flag|India}}
** {{Flag|Italy}}
** {{Flag|Japan}}
** {{Flag|South Korea}}
** {{Flag|Singapore}}
* 2017年5月11日，在美国[[阿拉斯加州|阿拉斯加州]][[费尔班克斯_(阿拉斯加州)|费尔班克斯]]召开的第十次部长级会议上，以下國家加入：<ref>{{Cite web|title=ARCTIC COUNCIL MINISTERS MEET, SIGN BINDING AGREEMENT ON SCIENCE COOPERATION, PASS CHAIRMANSHIP FROM U.S. TO FINLAND|url=https://arctic-council.org/en/news/arctic-council-ministers-meet-sign-binding-agreement-on-science-cooperation-pass-chairmanship-from-u.s-to-finland/|accessdate=2020-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200612151400/https://arctic-council.org/en/news/arctic-council-ministers-meet-sign-binding-agreement-on-science-cooperation-pass-chairmanship-from-u.s-to-finland/|archive-date=2020-06-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>
** {{Flag|Switzerland}}

2011年，理事會公佈觀察員的加入資格，當中包括需要承認北極國家在北極地區的主權和治權，認可建設[[北冰洋|北冰洋]]法律框架（例如海洋法）。<ref name="Buixade Farre 2014" />

==== 待定觀察員 ====
待定觀察員爲已經通過大部分參加條件的候選國。2013年[[基律纳|基律纳]]大會上，[[欧洲联盟|歐盟]]提出了加入要求。但由於部分歐盟國家禁止獵殺海豹，故請求暫未被通過。<ref name="EUAAC">{{cite web|title=The EU and the Arctic Council|url=http://www.ecfr.eu/article/commentary_the_eu_and_the_arctic_council3005|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181117004519/https://www.ecfr.eu/article/commentary_the_eu_and_the_arctic_council3005|archive-date=November 17, 2018}}</ref>

目前的待定觀察員有

* {{Flag|European Union}}<ref name="arcticcouncilobservers2">{{cite web|title=Observers|url=https://arctic-council.org/about/observers/|access-date=September 15, 2021|publisher=Arctic Council Secretariat (2021). Arctic Council|archive-date=2022-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220529151107/https://www.arctic-council.org/about/observers/}}</ref>
* {{Flag|Turkey}}<ref>{{cite web|title=Turkey raises profile to be a polar power with expeditions|url=https://www.dailysabah.com/turkey/turkey-raises-profile-to-be-a-polar-power-with-expeditions/news|access-date=September 17, 2021|date=May 21, 2020|publisher=[[Daily_Sabah|Daily Sabah]]|archive-date=2022-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220321073504/https://www.dailysabah.com/turkey/turkey-raises-profile-to-be-a-polar-power-with-expeditions/news}}</ref>

待定觀察員和永久觀察員的分別是，永久觀察員會自動獲邀出席所有會議（雖然它們未必會全部參與），待定觀察員出席每一次會議都需要批准（雖然批准已屬例行形式）。

=== 北極原住民族參與組織 ===
在八個正式成員國當中，有七個擁有數量可觀的原住民族，冰島是唯一沒有原住民族居住的成員國。所有北極原住民族組織均可獲永久參與員地位，<ref name="Buixade Farre 2014" />但需滿足以下任一條件：代表世居在多於一個北極國家的某一原著民族，或代表某一北極國家內，兩個或多於兩個以上的世居原住民族。原住民族參與組織的數量需要在任何時候都小於正式成員國的數量。原住民族參與組織能夠參加理事會的一切活動。

截至2021年，共有六個北極原住民族參與組織：

* {{link-Wikidata|Q43895284|阿留申國際協會}}：代表俄羅斯和美國[[阿拉斯加州|阿拉斯加]]內的[[阿留申人|阿留申人]]（約有1萬5000人）<ref>{{cite web|title=Aleut International Association|url=https://arctic-council.org/about/permanent-participants/aia/|access-date=September 17, 2021|publisher=Arctic Council|archive-date=2022-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220529151103/https://www.arctic-council.org/about/permanent-participants/aia/}}</ref>
* {{link-Wikidata|Q30263298|北極阿薩巴斯卡議會}}：代表加拿大內（[[西北地区_(加拿大)|西北地區]]和[[育空地區|育空]]）和美國[[阿拉斯加州|阿拉斯加]]內使用阿薩巴斯卡人（約有4萬5000人）<ref>{{cite web|title=Arctic Athabaskan Council|url=https://arctic-council.org/about/permanent-participants/aac/|access-date=September 17, 2021|publisher=Arctic Council|archive-date=2022-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220529151109/https://www.arctic-council.org/about/permanent-participants/aac/}}</ref>
* {{link-Wikidata|Q30263327|哥威迅國際議會}}：代表加拿大內（[[西北地区_(加拿大)|西北地區]]和[[育空地區|育空]]）和美國[[阿拉斯加州|阿拉斯加]]內的[[哥威迅人|哥威迅人]]（約有9000人）<ref>{{cite web|title=Gwich'in Council International|url=https://arctic-council.org/about/permanent-participants/gci/|access-date=September 17, 2021|publisher=Arctic Council|archive-date=2022-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220529151108/https://www.arctic-council.org/about/permanent-participants/gci/}}</ref>
* [[因紐特人北極圈理事會|因纽特北極圈議會]]：代表加拿大、格陵蘭島、俄羅斯[[楚科奇自治区|楚科奇自治區和美國]][[阿拉斯加州|阿拉斯加]]內的[[因纽特人|因紐特人]]（約有18萬人）<ref>{{cite web|title=Gwich'in Council International|url=https://arctic-council.org/about/permanent-participants/icc/|access-date=September 17, 2021|publisher=Arctic Council|archive-date=2022-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220529151103/https://www.arctic-council.org/about/permanent-participants/icc/}}</ref>
* {{link-ru|俄羅斯北方原住民族協會|Ассоциация коренных малочисленных народов Севера, Сибири и Дальнего Востока Российской Федерации}}：代表居住在俄羅斯[[西伯利亚|西伯利亞]]、[[俄羅斯遠東地區|遠東地區]]和極北地區的北方原住民（約有25萬人）<ref>{{cite web|title=Russian Association of Indigenous Peoples of the North|url=https://arctic-council.org/about/permanent-participants/raipon/|access-date=September 17, 2021|publisher=Arctic Council|archive-date=2022-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220529151105/https://www.arctic-council.org/about/permanent-participants/raipon/}}</ref>
* [[薩米理事會|薩米理事會]]：代表芬蘭、挪威、瑞典和俄羅斯內的[[萨米人|薩米人]]（約有10萬人）<ref>{{cite web|title=Saami Council|url=https://arctic-council.org/about/permanent-participants/saami-council/|access-date=September 17, 2021|publisher=Arctic Council|archive-date=2022-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220321073542/https://arctic-council.org/about/permanent-participants/saami-council/}}</ref>

以上組織由{{Link-en|北極理事會原住民祕書處|Arctic Council Indigenous Peoples Secretariat}}管理。<ref name="about5">{{cite web|title=About the Arctic Council|url=https://arctic-council.org/about/|access-date=September 17, 2021|date=April 7, 2011|publisher=The Arctic Council|archive-date=2022-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220529151058/https://www.arctic-council.org/about/}}</ref>

=== 觀察組織 ===
北極理事會同時也對[[政府间组织|政府間組織]]、{{Link-en|議會間組織|Inter-parliamentary institutions}}和[[非政府组织|非政府組織]]開放，並對其授予觀察組織地位。<ref name="arcticcouncilobservers3">{{cite web|title=Observers|url=https://arctic-council.org/about/observers/|access-date=September 15, 2021|publisher=Arctic Council Secretariat (2021). Arctic Council|archive-date=2022-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220529151107/https://www.arctic-council.org/about/observers/}}</ref>目前有以下觀察組織：極地區議員會議<ref>{{cite web|title=Arctic Parliamentarians|url=http://www.arcticparl.org/|access-date=2013-09-24|publisher=Arcticparl.org|archive-date=2015-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150321110618/http://www.arcticparl.org/}}</ref>、[[國際自然保護聯盟|國際自然保護聯盟]]、[[國際紅十字會|國際紅十字會]]、[[北歐理事會|北歐理事會]]、北方論壇<ref>{{cite web|title=Northern Forum|url=http://www.northernforum.org|access-date=2013-09-24|publisher=Northern Forum|archive-date=2017-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171108060859/http://www.northernforum.org/}}</ref>、[[联合国开发计划署|聯合國開發計劃署]]、[[联合国环境署|聯合國環境署]]、世界驯鹿牧民协会<ref name="reindeerherders">{{Cite web|title=Association of World Reindeer Herders|url=http://arcticportal.org/portal/icr-new/assn.-of-world-reindeer-herders|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070928200138/http://arcticportal.org/portal/icr-new/assn.-of-world-reindeer-herders|archive-date=September 28, 2007|url-status=dead}}</ref>、[[北極大學|北極大學]]、[[世界自然基金會|世界自然基金會]]北極規劃小組。

== 行政 ==

=== 會議 ===
[[File:Finnish_Foreign_Minister_Timo_Soini_at_the_Arctic_Council_Ministerial_(47006335634).jpg|thumb]]
北極理事會每六個月在主席國家召開一次資深北極官員會議。資深北極官員是八個成員國的高層代表，通常爲外交官或其他高階外交部官員。會議同時邀請六個原住民族組織及觀察員的代表。

在兩年任期結束之前，輪任主席會召開部長級會議，對其任內的工作作到任總結。與會者一般爲成員八個成員國的外交部、北方事務部或環境部部長。

每次部長級會議都有以當地城市為名的宣言。該宣言會歸納理事會過去的成就和對未來的展望，一般會涵蓋氣候改變、可持續發展、北極監督和評估、北極永久生物污染物及其他污染物等主要議題，還有六個工作小組的工作總結。

