=== 輪任主席國 ===
理事會每兩年更換一次主席國。<ref name="HillNotes">{{cite web|title=Canada as Chair of the Arctic Council|url=http://www.parl.gc.ca/Content/LOP/ResearchPublications/2013-20-e.htm|access-date=2013-09-06|date=May 1, 2013|last=Troniak|first=Shauna|website=HillNotes|publisher=Library of Parliament Research Publications|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130629023119/http://parl.gc.ca/Content/LOP/ResearchPublications/2013-20-e.htm|archive-date=2013-06-29|url-status=dead}}</ref>目前主席國爲俄羅斯，其任期至2023年。<ref name="Iceland Chairmanship">{{cite web|title=Iceland Chairs Arctic Council|url=https://icelandmonitor.mbl.is/news/politics_and_society/2019/05/07/iceland_chairs_arctic_council/|access-date=2019-05-07|archive-date=2022-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220525214744/https://icelandmonitor.mbl.is/news/politics_and_society/2019/05/07/iceland_chairs_arctic_council/}}</ref>

