=== 祕書處 ===
每任主席國負責理事會祕書處的運行。祕書處負責處理理事會的行政事務，其職責包括，組織半年會議、管理議會網站以及分發報告和文件。由於三個北歐國家挪威、丹麥和瑞典達成一致意見共享祕書處，<ref name="AC 20186">{{Cite web|title=Arctic Council Secretariat|url=https://www.arctic-council.org/index.php/en/about-us/arctic-council/the-arctic-council-secretariat|access-date=2018-01-22|website=Arctic Council|language=en-gb|archive-date=2022-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220503090202/https://www.arctic-council.org/index.php/en/about-us/arctic-council/the-arctic-council-secretariat}}</ref>挪威北極學院曾於2007年至2013年連續六年間承擔祕書處工作，工作人員亦來自以上三國。

部分成員國希望建立常設秘書處，但[[美國|美國]]自北極理事會成立開始就一直否決這建議。最終在2012年，理事會決定在挪威[[特罗姆瑟|特罗姆瑟]]設立常任祕書處。<ref>{{cite web|title=Travel of Deputy Secretary Burns to Sweden and Estonia|url=https://2009-2017.state.gov/r/pa/prs/ps/2012/05/189840.htm|access-date=2013-09-24|date=2012-05-14|publisher=State.gov|archive-date=2022-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220321073453/https://2009-2017.state.gov/r/pa/prs/ps/2012/05/189840.htm}}</ref><ref name="Buixade Farre 2014" />

=== 北極理事會原住民祕書處 ===
對於六個原住民組織而言，若每次理事會召開會議都派出代表與會（尤其會議地點會在各北極城市間變動），將會對其組成較大的財政負擔。爲解決其囧景，同時鼓勵原住民組織積極參與理事會的工作，理事會對原住民祕書處提供財政支持。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Terms, Reference and Guidelines|url=http://arctic-council.org/filearchive/IPS%20Terms%20of%20Reference%20and%20Guidelines.pdf|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110720000949/http://arctic-council.org/filearchive/IPS%20Terms%20of%20Reference%20and%20Guidelines.pdf|archive-date=2011-07-20|url-status=dead}}</ref>

=== 工作小組 ===
北極理事會的實際工作是由轄下的六个工作小組負責
*北極監督和評估計畫<ref name="amap">{{cite web|title=Arctic Monitoring and Assessment Programme|url=http://www.amap.no/|access-date=2013-09-24|publisher=Amap.no|archive-date=2006-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061022214206/http://www.amap.no/}}</ref>（英文：Arctic Monitoring and Assessment Programme，縮寫 AMAP）
*北極理事會控污行動計劃<ref>{{cite web|title=Arctic Contaminants Action Program (ACAP)|url=http://acap.arctic-council.org/|access-date=2013-09-24|publisher=Acap.arctic-council.org|archive-date=2013-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130628144120/http://www.acap.arctic-council.org/}}</ref>（英文：Arctic Contaminants Action Program，縮寫 ACAP）
*北極動植物保育<ref>{{cite web|title=Conservation of Arctic Flora & Fauna (CAFF)|url=http://www.caff.is/|access-date=2013-09-24|website=Caff.is|publisher=Conservation of Arctic Flora and Fauna|archive-date=2006-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061126184623/http://www.caff.is/}}</ref>（英文：Conservation of Arctic Flora & Fauna，縮寫 CAFF）
*緊急、預防、準備暨應變<ref name="eppr">{{cite web|title=Emergency Prevention, Preparedness & Response|url=http://eppr.arctic-council.org/|access-date=2013-09-24|date=2013-06-04|publisher=Eppr.arctic-council.org|archive-date=2007-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070311000941/http://eppr.arctic-council.org/}}</ref>（英文：Emergency Prevention, Preparedness & Response，縮寫 EPPR）
*北極海洋環境保護<ref name="pame">{{cite web|title=Protection of the Arctic Marine Environment|url=http://www.pame.is/|access-date=2013-09-24|date=2013-06-13|publisher=Pame.is|archive-date=2006-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061209215420/http://www.pame.is/}}</ref><ref name="pame22">{{Cite web|title=Oops! We couldn't find this page for you|url=https://arcticportal.org/page-not-found|last=User|first=Super|website=Arctic Portal|access-date=2021-12-31|archive-date=2022-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220601092826/https://arcticportal.org/page-not-found}}</ref>（英文：Protection of the Arctic Marine Environmen，縮寫 PAME）
* -{zh-hant:永續;zh-hans:可持续}-發展工作組 <ref name="sdwg">{{cite web|title=Sustainable Development Working Group|url=http://portal.sdwg.org/|access-date=2013-09-24|date=2013-08-27|publisher=Portal.sdwg.org|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130114204240/http://portal.sdwg.org/|archive-date=2013-01-14|url-status=dead}}</ref>（英文：Sustainable Development Working Group，縮寫 SDWG）

